MicroPython license and copyright
=================================

This file describes the licensing and copyright conditions for the source
code found in this repository.

The core MicroPython source code is licensed under the MIT license and has
various copyright holders.  These copyright holders are usually mentioned
explicitly in each file, on a file-by-file basis.

There is also third party source code in this repository, either included
directly or via a git submodule.  Such source code has its own license and
copyright, which can be found alongside that component.

The following sections describe the licensing and copyright in more detail.

