----------------------------------------------

MicroPython includes third-party software that is licensed under different
terms. These licenses are summarized in the tree below, please refer to these
files and directories for further license and copyright information.

/ (MIT)
    /drivers
        /cc3000 (BSD-3-clause)
        /cc3100 (BSD-3-clause)
        /wiznet5k (BSD-3-clause)
